Subterranea is back with our 52nd episode, beautiful artist all the way from Miami, USA @dj_milarubio 🇺🇸 She delivered this amazing guest mix absolutely brand new ID’s and we can’t wait until you listen to it. For our show she prepared some real thumping beats from start to finish. A cosmic, energetic and highly driving melodic techno mix in which she converted her energy, love and passion. And that's just the way we like it! 💜

Mila Rubio is a music producer and DJing with over 12 years experience. She produce melodic progressive and techno music. As a special guest headliner, she performed at the after-party of FIFA 2018 in Russia and entered the list top 10 DJ’s in Russia 2019 according to Djanetop.com.  With a unique talent inspired by Kyiv, where she was born, she made a name for herself. She brings her unique and deep music to different places and cultures around the world, moving and inspiring them with her passion for music. ✨

Don’t wait much longer and find the Link in bio. This mix for those who live for the thrill of the underground. So buckle up as we take you on a wild ride, and let the distorted beats take control! Swipe up left to find out the ID’s 👋

Fantastic news for everyone! My long-awaited tracks "Blink Water" and "Galaxy Trip" are released on the respected @bunnytigerofficial label on October 20th. From melodic to trance, these tunes will transport you to my musical universe. Embark on an unforgettable journey and don’t forget to share your feedback in the comments!

The long-awaited day has come: my new track “Blink Water” has officially appeared on @bunnytigerofficial ! Explore my realm of melodic techno by listening to it. To access the track, click on the link in my profile header. I hope, you like it!
